{"tid":1865891,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好想下世做隻狗狗","createTime":"2020-02-06T12:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T14:43:07.000Z","uid":29949,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a0bccd21001a9f976fc62b7730e6b77f951c1e37","tid":1865891,"uid":29949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:11:10.000Z","msg":"做人真係好攰 <br />\n我都唔知到底係喺香港做人好攰定真係本身做人都係攰<br />\n因為我冇試過去其他國家生活 所以真係冇得比較<br />\n定係每個人性格唔同 思維唔同 <br />\n所以有d人會冇咁辛苦 冇咁攰？<br />\n我都唔知 因為我諗性格呢味野都唔係話改就改<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時會諗<br />\n可能你覺得你愛既人唔夠重視你 剩係掛住同朋友玩<br />\n剩係掛住自己開心 唔理你開唔開心 佢真係好自私<br />\n但換個角度<br />\n你想你另一半樣樣放你係第一位 <br />\n成日都陪住你 唔出去social 唔出去玩<br />\n你一樣都係咁自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又或者你為人父母 想你子女讀好書<br />\n想佢地搵到錢 想佢地孝順對你好<br />\n其實都一樣自私 因為你冇諗過到底佢地想做d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底應該點樣做人先至係對另一半/家人最好<br />\n到底點樣做先至算對自己好<br />\n<br />\n做人真係好複雜<br />\n如果可以 我真係好想下世做隻有人養既狗狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以痴住自己鍾意既人/屋企人 又可以同佢地一齊住<br />\n有得食有得訓就好滿足 唔駛諗咁多野<br />\n好似好開心咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人都曾經有呢個想法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4882abd24af3705228c0241fe703c967b72aa6","tid":1865891,"uid":36435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:12:45.000Z","msg":"做大陸狗會俾人煲黎食。。"},{"pid":"a88474e59c4a0c0613a1eecb52ca5be76ef779fa","tid":1865891,"uid":29949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b4882abd24af3705228c0241fe703c967b72aa6","tid":1865891,"uid":36435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:12:45.000Z","msg":"做大陸狗會俾人煲黎食。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:14:21.000Z","msg":"做狗都要揀岩地方出世先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2249b54e7ae2aba25f3cde5130b8f00c19212adc","tid":1865891,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a88474e59c4a0c0613a1eecb52ca5be76ef779fa","tid":1865891,"uid":29949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b4882abd24af3705228c0241fe703c967b72aa6","tid":1865891,"uid":36435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:12:45.000Z","msg":"做大陸狗會俾人煲黎食。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:14:21.000Z","msg":"做狗都要揀岩地方出世先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:20:00.000Z","msg":"閹左你"},{"pid":"6e512c491b1f68359b7f7eba1fe42ed0ef428014","tid":1865891,"uid":196701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:32:20.000Z","msg":"繼續做曱甴"},{"pid":"b8d680c24cae9b0c282acb0df2ef62e9910e4fa3","tid":1865891,"uid":29949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e512c491b1f68359b7f7eba1fe42ed0ef428014","tid":1865891,"uid":196701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:32:20.000Z","msg":"繼續做曱甴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T14:43:07.000Z","msg":"帶埋屋企隻狗狗一齊出去做"}]}